    'anatomy': 'It is a dark, finless, snake-like creature measuring 25 to 30 feet in length. It features a slender, football-shaped head resembling a horse, and biological flippers for steering. Biologists note that alleged sightings frequently lack undulating serpentine motion, instead matching the \'smooth footprint\' left by marine mammals.',
